Kitchen Operations & Hours
Our downstairs area (open to the beach where the bands play) is open 11am - 2am every day of the week. Our kitchen is open until 1am.
Our upstairs area (enclosed with A/C and great views) is open 11:30am - 11pm Sunday thru Thursday and 11:30am - 12 midnight Friday and Saturday.
